## Both vendored blobs exceed the project's "<=10 MB committable" rule.
## They are fetched on demand via fetch.ps1 (idempotent; sha256 pinned
## against the upstream Debian SHA256SUMS file). SHA256SUMS is committed
## so the boot test and reproducibility gate can verify integrity
## without re-running fetch.ps1.
vmlinuz-debian-netinst
initrd.img-debian-netinst
